        "AHP Consistency Analysis\n",
        "The initial pairwise comparison matrices were constructed following Saaty (1990), using a 1–9 ratio scale to express the relative importance of criteria. Following standard AHP procedure, the Consistency Ratio (CR) was calculated for each matrix to verify the logical coherence of the judgements. A CR ≤ 0.10 is considered acceptable (Saaty, 1990).\n",
