        "# ============================================================\n",
        "# CELL 9 — FAHP Weights — Buckley Method\n",
        "# Recalculates FAHP weights using Buckley's (1985) geometric\n",
        "# mean method, which produces more reliable priority vectors\n",
        "# than Chang's extent analysis and avoids rank reversals.\n",
